A man reportedly broke into the family s shack in Angelo informal settlement in Ekurhuleni in an apparent robbery attempt, the Boksburg Advertiser reports.One of the family members woke up and realised they were in the company of an uninvited guest.The family member grabbed a steel bar and smashed the intruder on the head, leaving him injured. After hitting the intruder, the resident heard a commotion outside and saw a group of people running away.The police arrived and found the injured intruder and a gun on the floor next to the door.The firearm was confiscated and the suspect taken to hospital, where he received treatment under police guard.It is still unclear if the gun belongs to the intruder, but investigations continue.Read original story on boksburgadvertiser.co.za